    <div id="carousel">
        <img src="/img/cute-white-fur.jpg" class="active">
        <img src="/img/multicolor-heels.jpg">
        <img src="/img/shirt-and-shoes.jpg">
        <!-- Add more images as needed -->
    </div>
    <p class="imageCredit">All images gotten from Unsplash</p>
  <section id="why-puppies">
    <h2>Project Fashion?</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Project Fashion, where style meets community in the vibrant world of fashion! At Project Fashion, we believe that fashion is not just about clothing; it's a form of expression, creativity, and self-discovery. Our platform is designed to be a hub for fashion enthusiasts, a space where individuals can share their unique style, discover the latest trends, and engage in meaningful conversations about all things fashion.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Sounds Fun! What do I do to be a part of the community?</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Sign up: Create an account to become apart of our project fashion community!</li>
      <li>Upload image: Upload a fashion moment or outfit you want to talk about!</li>
      <li>Share your thoughts: Whether it's a simple critique, a way to improve the outfit or something you've seen, let us know your thoughts on it! </li>
      <li>Comment: You've shared your thoughts on your post, why not share it on other posts as well (intergration coming soon)</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section id="latest-posts">
    <h2>Latest Blog Posts</h2>
    <ul class="list-inline container text-center">
        <% posts.forEach((post) => { %>
            <li class="list-inline-item px-4">
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <img src="<%= post.image %>" class="card-img-top img-fluid" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title"><%= post.title %></h5>
                      <p class="card-text text-truncate"><%= post.description %></p>
                      <% if(!user) { %>
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-dark">Click to see more</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                          <a href="/post/<%= post._id %>" class="btn btn-dark">Click to see more</a>
                          <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        <% }); %>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="get-involved">
    <h2>Want to Get Involved?</h2>
    <p>Join our community of fashion lovers! Follow us on social media, subscribe to our newsletter, or contribute to our blog. We'd love to have you as part of the Project Fashion family!</p>
  </section>
  
